       "title": "央视报道：广众金融，新常态下的金融服务旗舰",
       "thumb_media_id": "uf-tBXRq7PN9u9wjlDPVQ-ynHPj0bfl6tIlAbQbQAm4",
       "author": "QTYD",
       "digest": "央视网：广众金融，广谋从众，众心如城。",
       "show_cover_pic": "1",
       "content": "<p style=\"\">什么是常态?曾经我们以为中国的经济会以双位数持续增长，事实上，中国双位数的经济增长态势的确持续了长达30年——这就是常态，在这一常态之下，从政府到民间，从国企到民企，精神处于高度紧张，唯恐出现纰漏，错过了机遇期。当我们心理松弛，不再以GDP唯命是从，但是GDP依然能够维持合理的增长区间，这就是新常态。“从旧常态到新常态的转变，不仅仅是‘一字之差’，更是企业、金融机构以及个人的集体转变”，浙江广众金融总经理于海坤先生表示。</p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/PJL6MwDWGtBVrJpgF1QCtrFueqZ0NuWyyfsvt8yNraSrjlT2C2yRk4IvHHwZia4HiaKTr9jKQWgqqyHNG0BjvW1A/0?wxfmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-w=\"500\" width=\"auto\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/PJL6MwDWGtBVrJpgF1QCtrFueqZ0NuWyyfsvt8yNraSrjlT2C2yRk4IvHHwZia4HiaKTr9jKQWgqqyHNG0BjvW1A/0?wxfmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"  /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">央视网原文：</p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); text-decoration: underline; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">http://yueyu.cntv.cn/2015/04/03/ARTI1428029104590863.shtml</span></p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">广众金融是一家专门从事金融服务外包的大型企业，注册资本2亿元。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />不可否认，当前的经济新常态是在旧常态的基础上发展而来，经济旧常态虽然有其弊端，例如发展质量不高、对环境损耗大，但是经济旧常态的功绩不可抹杀。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">经济旧常态的功绩</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />经济旧常态之下，最大的发展功绩就是巨量财富的积累，包括国家财富、个人财富以及企业财富的积累。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先看国家财富。</span></strong></p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">自从改革开放以来，中国GDP开始步入双位数增长通道，双位数增长持续了30年之久，被经济学家称之为“经济黄金30年”。双位数的经济增长直到近两年才被停止，步入个位数增长阶段。即使是个位数GDP增长，依然处于中高速增长阶段，与欧美发达国家经济增长相比，中国经济增速一直维持在发达国家两到三倍的水平。经济持续增长也意味着国家财富的不断被“窖藏”，而“窖藏”财富的仓库就是金融机构<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次看个人财富。</span></strong></p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">早从2003年开始，福布斯就开始每年定期发布中国富豪排行榜，十余年间，从未中断。将福布斯中国富豪排行榜与世界富豪排行榜进行对比，可以发现两个明显的规律，一是中国富豪进入世界富豪榜单的人数越来越多，二是中国富豪在世界富豪榜单中的排名越来越靠前。不可否认，今天的中国，依然是一个贫富差距较大的发展中国家，但是同样不可否认的一点是，中国家庭以及个人财富积累规模迅速膨胀。根据2014年发布的报告，当年中国家庭财富总量已经位居世界第三。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后看企业财富。</strong></span></p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">2005年6月6日，上证指数998点的时候，A股市值不到3万亿，但是到2014年12月12日，沪深两市总市值超过35万亿元，这一数据超越了日本，一举成为全球第二大股票市场。股票市值的巨大“盘子”和增长力度，也侧面反映出中国企业财富积累的情况。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />总量越大，前行愈加吃力，这是经济发展的固有规律，当国家、个人以及企业积累的巨量财富之后，如果要实现财富的持续增长，依靠原有的‘中国制造’发展模式，前行已经愈加艰难，此时就需要寻找新的模式”，于海坤表示。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />在广众金融看来，过去30年，我们的财富增长模式是制造，而在新常态，我们的财富增长模式需要转变为投资。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从制造到投资</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />纵观中国致富轨迹不难发现，中国正在步入致富发展的第三阶段——“三轨”并行时代。所谓“三轨”，即依靠低廉劳动力生财、依靠不可再生资源生财、依靠财富生财。其中，财富增长最快的轨迹，无疑是“依靠财富生财”。根据对财富生产的驱动因素观察，目前中国的财富增长已步入第三阶段，即以财生财、以服务生财阶段。前两个阶段可定义为以人为要素生财阶段，即主要靠劳动力或雇佣劳动力获取财富阶段的原始财富积累阶段，以资源等元素(如矿产资源、土地资源等)获取财富的第二阶段。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />但随着我国经济的发展和社会的进步，参照发达国家的经验，前两个阶段驱动财富增长的因素的边际效益在逐渐下降，必然要求有新的财富增长模式涌现。而这一新的财富增长模式就是“投资”，包括以银行为牵引动力的国家投资、以企业为主体的企业投资以及个人理财投资。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />如何引导银行、企业和个人进行高效投资?这固然需要国家更具治理智慧，银行需要转变发展思路，个人需要更具创新，但是更加需要领军的金融服务企业，敢于担当和作为。而这，正是浙江广众金融的使命所在<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />截止2015年3月，浙江广众金融集团旗下的祺天优贷已经累积投资金额接近千万，这一成绩不过是在两个月时间实现的，祺天优贷已经跃升为一流的P2P平台。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />未来的浙江广众金融集团，将通过持续的金融创新和管理创新，优化资源配置，提高核心竞争力，为中国银行、企业、个人提供全方位的金融服务。致力于成为中国最卓越的金融服务商。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  />广众金融，广谋从众，众心如城。</p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(155, 187, 89); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">祺</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 100, 162); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">天</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(75, 172, 198); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">优</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(247, 150, 70); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">贷</span>，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(75, 172, 198); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">快</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 100, 162); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">乐</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(155, 187, 89); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">理</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">财</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">帮您加薪15%！</p><p style=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"\">点击下方<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">阅读原文</span>8秒注册领取30元红包</p>",
